---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Nomudev" description="Privacy Policy and Cookie Statement for Nomudev.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-24 max-w-4xl text-text-muted">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-text-main font-mono mb-4">Privacy Policy & Cookie Protocol</h1>
      <p class="text-sm font-mono text-accent-blue">Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12 prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">1. System Identity (Introduction)</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to the Nomudev network. We respect your privacy and represent the "Truth" regarding how we handle your digital footprint. 
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and shield your information when you visit <strong>nomudev.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">2. Data Ingestion (Collection)</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal data necessary to maintain system integrity and improve user experience:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information on how you access the site (IP address, browser type, device info).</li>
          <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> If you contact us via email, we store the content of your message to reply.</li>
          <li><strong>Matrix Choice:</strong> We store a boolean value in your local storage indicating your preference for the "Red Pill" or "Blue Pill".</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">3. Usage Protocols (Purpose)</h2>
        <p>Your data is processed for the following directives:</p>
         <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>To provide and maintain our Service.</li>
          <li>To monitor the usage of our Service (Analytics).</li>
          <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">4. Cookie Matrix (Cookies)</h2>
        <p>
          We use "Cookies" (small data files) to track the activity on our Service.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-surface border border-border p-6 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-accent-green mb-2">Your Choices</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li>
                    <span class="text-red-500 font-bold font-mono">[RED PILL]</span>: 
                    Acceptance of all cookies, including tracking and analytics scripts to improve the platform.
                </li>
                <li>
                     <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold font-mono">[BLUE PILL]</span>: 
                     Rejection of non-essential cookies. You remain anonymous, but some advanced system features may be dormant.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">5. User Rights (GDPR/CCPA)</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you have rights regarding your data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li><strong>The Right to Access:</strong> You can request copies of your personal data.</li>
          <li><strong>The Right to Rectification:</strong> You can request correction of inaccurate information.</li>
          <li><strong>The Right to Erasure:</strong> You can request that we delete your data ("Blue Pill Protocol").</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4 font-mono">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this policy, please contact us via the main frequency:<br>
          <a href="mailto:contact@nomudev.com" class="text-accent-blue hover:text-accent-green transition-colors font-mono mt-2 inline-block">contact@nomudev.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="pt-12 border-t border-border mt-12">
          <a href="/" class="text-accent-blue hover:text-white transition-colors font-mono text-sm">&larr; Return to Main System</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
